Class ObservableBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.query.ObservableBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable<T>

    public final class ObservableBuilder<T>
extends Object
implements Observable<T>
    Wrapper object around an Observable which lets the user chain some Reactive operators.

    This builder is the dual of the IterableBuilder class.

    Author:
    akarnokd, Jan 25, 2012
